%section#cinema
  .white-background
    .container.content-section
      %hr
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
          %h3 Chiang Mai Cat Cinema Reservations
          %p.text-center
            %br
            With a cat cinema booking, you get the cinema room plus cats, popcorn and coke for a two hours timeslot. You can either bring your own movie or enjoy a sci-fi or horro classic on our 100" screen and surround sound system.
      .row
        .col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2.centered
          %table.table.table-striped
            %thead
              %tr
                %th.text-center Package
                %th.text-center Description
                %th.text-center Date and time
            %tbody

              %tr
                %td
                  %b Movie Classics
                %td.text-left
                  %ul
                    Enjoy a surprise classic in the company of our cats. Popcorn and soft drinks included! 
                    %br
                    %br
                    Pricing: THB 250 / person
                %td
                  Can be booked any day between 10:00am and 5:00pm.
              %tr
                %td
                  %b Bring-Your-Own-Movie-Pack
                %td.text-left
                  %ul
                    Bring your own DVD, Bluray or USB drive to watch a movie with cats. Popcorn and soft drinks included!
                    %br
                    %br
                    Pricing: THB 250 / person
                %td
                  Can be booked any day between 10:00am and 5:00pm.

          %p.text-center
            %a{ :href => "/chiangmai/booking", target: '_blank'}
              %button.btn.btn-success Book now!
          %p.small.text-center 
            * Outside food and drinks are not allowed. Customers must bring their own movies on DVD, Bluray, or USB drive.


            For questions and bookings via phone, you can call us at 092-273-1011.